==English==

===Proper noun===
'''Superman'''

# Name of a [[comic book|comic-book]] character (his real name is Kael) from the planet Krypton who, while under Earth's yellow sun, has "super" powers (e.g., the ability to fly, super strength, tough skin, heat vision, and extreme speed).  He poses as a mild-mannered human named Clark Kent.
s.<!--note that "comic-book" is hyphenated here as it is a noun being used to modify another; "comic" refers to the book, not to the character--><!--Um, shouldn't American hyphenation rules be used for such a very American term?--> 2. A 
